=========
VLE 2.0.0
=========

:Info See <http://www.vle-project.org/> for introductory docs.
:Author: Gauthier Quesnel <quesnel@users.sourceforge.net>

VLE2 is a tiny library designed to quickly develop DEVS, DSDE simulator.

Requirements
------------

Must have:

- c++ compiler (support for C++11)
- libc++ or libstdc++ (support for C++11)
- boost (1.49 or better)

Optional requirements:

- libarchive (3 or better)

Compiling and installing
------------------------

  ./configure
  make
(do this as root unless you are installing in your users directories):
  make install
